00:00:17.374 --> 00:00:27.021
Some things we can change, and some things we can't. People say, "How accurate are you? How much is the Lord?

00:00:27.022 --> 00:00:40.425
You're just saying all this stuff and there's nothing to it."I get all kinds of crazy emails, so I'm going to show you some of the things that are coming to pass because you haven't known me that long.

00:00:40.426 --> 00:00:48.398
