00:01:24.899 --> 00:01:29.552
You need to know these are demonic forces; these are demons.

00:01:29.553 --> 00:01:36.715
It's fallen angel stuff, not aliens. There's no such thing as aliens; it's demons.

00:01:36.716 --> 00:01:56.194
It is a great deception to try to explain away where the body of Christ goes when the Rapture of the church takes place."I waited through 2014, 2015, 2016, and 2017, and there was nothing really in the news.

00:01:56.195 --> 00:02:06.107
Now, here we are in 2024, and we are having what people call Nephilim encounters in Miami.

00:02:06.108 --> 00:02:10.203
