00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:08.918
The Lord warned me to pray against this rocket attached to a barge.

00:03:08.919 --> 00:03:19.245
The barge was shooting a rocket off that had an EMP on it—an electromagnetic pulse—to try to cause darkness.

00:03:19.246 --> 00:03:26.039
It went out of the Mississippi into the Gulf of Mexico. It was supposed to be carrying oats or some kind of grain.

00:03:26.040 --> 00:03:39.113
If you look at when the grain harvest takes place in America, it's usually in early to late summer.

00:03:39.114 --> 00:03:54.757
For the first time ever, I was scanning YouTube and noticed in my feed it says China is practicing launching rockets from boats.

00:03:54.758 --> 00:04:01.604
It shows the rocket shooting off from the barge into outer space.

00:04:01.605 --> 00:04:05.518
They're practicing this. Why would they all of a sudden start doing this?

00:04:05.519 --> 00:04:20.916
This is not a coincidence. This is exactly what the Spirit of the Lord tried to warn you about. These men on this boat were Asian-looking.

00:04:20.917 --> 00:04:37.879
They were from Asia; I have no idea if it was China or whatever, but it's the same culture and people the Lord showed me on the boat.

00:04:37.880 --> 00:04:48.999
It's coming to pass; it's in the news. Prophecy 3: The Lord warned me about the two-state solution.

