00:05:09.659 --> 00:05:23.245
This happened just two or three days ago. Another word I warned about is the eclipse coming in April, which is a major sign.

00:05:23.246 --> 00:05:40.517
I told you there were clouds and lightning, and it was freezing. I said it was very odd the way this eclipse was darkened out.

00:05:40.517 --> 00:05:48.066
The Lord was warning me about this eclipse; it's very serious to be praying over these things.

00:05:48.067 --> 00:06:12.067
I'm not telling you this to cause fear, but to warn the prayer warriors who know how to stand in the gap.

00:06:12.068 --> 00:06:24.433
