00:06:24.434 --> 00:06:34.489
I warned you in the World War III video that Turkey was beating the drums.

00:06:34.490 --> 00:06:42.083
I saw huge war drums in the spirit, and I said Turkey will get involved.

00:06:42.084 --> 00:07:18.366
I saw a demonic-looking fallen angel coming out of a pit with a Viking helmet and a war sash, creating war all over Europe and messing with Putin.

00:07:18.367 --> 00:07:26.411
Then I saw men with red hats marching towards Israel to cause destruction.

00:07:26.412 --> 00:07:40.224
I believe those are either Turkish fighters or Hezbollah. I prophesied the war in Israel before it started.

00:07:40.225 --> 00:08:00.472
I also saw the fires in Hawaii before they manifested. Do I still believe there's more with Hawaii?

00:08:00.473 --> 00:08:17.723
Yes, I do. There are surprise attacks like Pearl Harbor; it's not over.

00:08:17.724 --> 00:08:41.543
