00:10:54.557 --> 00:11:36.390
I warned you they would keep extending lawsuits against Donald Trump through the summer. I saw a major red MAGA on the hats rising up even more.

00:11:36.391 --> 00:11:45.124
We saw that already in Iowa; it was one of the largest turnouts in that state's history for the Republican Party.

00:11:45.125 --> 00:12:37.569
