00:20:19.301 --> 00:20:25.848
It's awesome to be in the last days, ladies and gentlemen. Jesus is coming, and I hope you're ready.

00:20:25.849 --> 00:20:35.113
We see the signs of the times every day, all the time. Things are happening, from deceptions to all kinds of stuff.

00:20:35.114 --> 00:20:43.899
