00:22:31.962 --> 00:22:37.274
He died for you and he's on the right hand of the Father right now, making intercession for you.

00:22:37.275 --> 00:22:42.958
That's all you've got to do: believe what he said he did for you.

00:22:42.959 --> 00:22:50.805
Go read John over and over again. I just want to encourage you all today. Let me pray for you all.

00:22:50.806 --> 00:22:55.617
Father, I just thank you for your hand on every single person here today.

